J. A. Preston https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/J._A._Preston 0 James Allen Preston Sr.. (born November 13, 1932), known professionally as J. A. Preston is an American actor. Preston is best known for his role as Ozzie Cleveland on the NBC primetime television series Hill Street Blues which originally aired from 1981 until 1987. James_Allen_Preston_Sr. .
